message.en_US: Is everyone ready?
I can't believe I agreed to do this.
You have chosen the side of justice, Spheromancer Shizuka!
Monsieur Grasshead!\. Here we all are, d'accord?
You really wanted to do this \c[3]guild war\c[0] with us that bad, oui?
First Scholars!\! The time has come to prove yourselves!
By doing battle against your guild...
It shall be determined today...
Whether you all walk\. the path\! of Justice!
PVP Combat!\! Activate!
Score one for us!
We're close to winning!
You've won the battle,\. but you have yet to win the war!
Sacrebleu!\. This is crazy!
Stick with me, Lukas!\. It's time for our \c[3]secret strategy\c[0]!
Such techniques are beyond mere Tribladers, we shall see!
Is that all, Spheromancer Lea?
Looks like it's a win for the \c[3]First Scholars\c[0]!
You guys put up a good fight!
Although I couldn't help but notice many \c[1]questionable\c[0] strategies at play,
I suppose the First Scholars won the day.
Mon Dieu!\. That was too much to handle.
It would appear that justice has been served!
Why must it always be so black and white to you?
As defenders of justice, we must always remain vigilant!
